data.description: Large 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath Farm House on approx 2 acres!  Just minutes to Metro, is close to schools, shopping, and employment.  Replacement windows throughout, this home has been lovingly restored.  The furnace and A/C are approx 5 years, the newer upgraded appliances in the kitchen remain, the washer and dryer stay too, in addition to a large bedroom set in the upstairs Master Bedroom.  A creek boarders the back of the property, a 1 car detached garage sits to the left of the home, and a large RV pole-barn, with room for 4 to 6 cars, is situated to the right.  Just a stone's throw from the caution light in Borden, so just a short drive to town.  Potential Bed & Breakfast!  Call this place home, and call us today to schedule your private showing!
